sequenceDiagram
    participant HW as esp_hardware
    participant UART as UART2
    participant LO as esp_logic
    participant ACT as Actuators

    loop Cyclic operation
        HW->>HW: Sample sensors
        HW->>UART: MSG_SENSOR_DATA frame
        UART->>LO: Receive and validate
        LO->>LO: Update sensor snapshot
        LO->>LO: Run control logic
        LO->>UART: MSG_ACTUATOR_CMD frame
        UART->>HW: Receive and validate
        HW->>ACT: Apply actuator command
    end

    alt Command timeout on esp_hardware
        HW->>ACT: Apply failsafe state
    end
